sushiswap.description: Sushi is a community-driven organization built to solve what might be  called the 'liquidity problem.' While other solutions provide incrementally progressive advances toward solving the problem of liquidity, Sushi's progress is intended to create a broader range of  network effects. Rather than limiting itself to a single solution, Sushi intertwines many decentralized markets and instruments.

haven-s-compass.description: In the heart-pounding world of Haven's Compass, players step into the boots of an operative of their choice in a dystopian future, where they are tasked with unraveling a conspiracy that threatens to plunge the world into chaos. Set against a backdrop of stunningly rendered post-apocalyptic landscapes, Haven's Compass seamlessly blends intense gunplay with a gripping narrative, immersing players in a cinematic experience like never before. As players choose their operative, each with a unique background and skill set, they navigate through intricately designed levels, battling relentless waves of enemies and utilizing an arsenal of futuristic weapons, each with its own unique abilities and upgrades. The game's dynamic AI adapts to players' strategies, ensuring a challenging and unpredictable combat experience that rewards both precision and tactical thinking.

chainguardians.description: Welcome to ChainGuardians, a player-driven platform revolutionizing the gaming world! By combining traditional gaming concepts with emerging technologies, we've created an ecosystem where players can earn rewards through our free-to-play digital asset mining platform and Role-Playing Game. But we don't stop there - we're constantly forming partnerships and working collaboratively to smash through ideological barriers oppressing user ownership and digital economies.

heroes-battle-arena.description: Multichain Play-and-earn Strategic RPG with zero start investments based on NFTs for the army, magic stones, gods and guilds power. Well known problem of P2E games is the need for significant initial investment. Our game solves this problem with free initial units, low-cost entry payment and a large base of opportunities to increase own income. Our game is based on interaction with NFTs, allowing us to connect the additional project to our game and many blockchains. Our game has 3 types of assets: battle units, magic stones and gods. The gameplay of our game is based on two types of battles: standard and premium. In standard battle, users can set the army on the battleground and look at how to work the auto-battle system. In premium type, users get full control of each step in each battle.

spells-of-genesis.description: As the first blockchain-based mobile game ever made, Spells of Genesis (SoG) combines trading card game (TCG) functionalities with the point-and-shoot aspects of arcade games. It was launched in April 2017 after a successful ICO, one of the first of its kind. Players have to collect and combine cards to create the strongest deck in order to fight their enemies in a series of battles. Associating deck-building strategy with an easy and intuitive gameplay, Spells of Genesis has already attracted numerous players around the world and the game is surrounded and supported by a strong community of players and fans. SoG is using two types of cards: in-game cards and blockchain cards.

world-of-dypians.description: The World of Dypians (WoD) is a massive multiplayer online role-playing game that is  set in a vast digital environment. Its target audience is individuals who enjoy playing  online games and exploring immersive digital environments. The goals of the game  are to provide players with a rich and engaging experience that allows them to  interact with others, complete quests, and engage in battles. WoD's unique  combination of fantasy and blockchain technology creates an exciting and dynamic  environment for players to explore and experience. The ultimate goal of the game is  to create a virtual world that is alive with activity, where players can form  communities, create their own content, and engage in meaningful interactions with  one another.    World of Dypians is built to support multiple blockchains, making it accessible and  interoperable with a wider audience. We aim to have a sustainable ecosystem where  users can contribute to the growth and development of the world. The multi-chain  integration and the wide range of offerings, including next-gen integrations like other  chains, tokens, NFTs, and a marketplace, make World of Dypians a cutting-edge  solution in the DeFi and metaverse space.
